body:
I think all tests passed now.

The error related to `MacOS CPU Tests` is the timeout of 
```
//tensorflow/python/kernel_tests:slice_op_test
```
, which I assume it is unrelated.

For `Ubuntu contrib` failure, it is:
```
ERROR: command succeeded, but there were errors parsing the target pattern
...
All tests passed but there were other errors during the build.
```
Maybe it is unrelated as well?
